show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/5U8HU9
show.description: He’s back to avenge his father’s death — and this time, he’s not holding back. Feared by many, he’s known as the Lord of the North, a warrior forged in ice and rage. With blood on his hands and fire in his heart, he’s here to reclaim his legacy… and crush every enemy that stands in his way.
